Package io.elegie.luchess.core.api.explore

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GameFindQuery
    A query to find certain game, by its id.
    GameFindQueryResult
    The result of the query, which may contain the searched game.
    GameListQuery
    A query to find a list of games, matching given criteria, including pagination.
    GameListQueryResult
    Returns the page of games, matching the criteria specified in the query.
    Query<T extends QueryResult>
    Specifies a domain query to be performed against the index.
    QueryResult
    A query result.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    QueryException
    When the query cannot be created or executed.
